<br>
Pull with malisement, sic pet, cast EM.<br>
<br>
In the time it takes to cast EM, your pet should get off at least one taunt, which will cause it to hold aggro as the EM spell hits.<br>
<br>
Sit for a moment, consider healing pet, then nuke as necessary. <p>Naladini <BR>
